{"tid":2124603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"知唔知為人清廉，治世之能臣嘅曹操會食咩海鮮？","createTime":"2020-07-25T13:30:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T13:43:52.000Z","uid":229502,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c71bda646b65eeaeb9b3c4ab190e4d92187eb2aa","tid":2124603,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T13:30:02.000Z","msg":"答案係!! 金爺海鮮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為曹操成世人都好清潔 即係曹永廉(曹操永遠廉正)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而曹永廉最近上電視推銷「金爺海鮮」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以!!!!!!! 答案就係金爺海鮮喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2KAbK5D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2KAbK5D.jpg&h=49177b72&s={SIZE}\" /> 輕鬆 謝謝大家 <strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">Too Long Didn't Read：派嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong> <p class=\"center\">💎金爺海鮮速遞💎 <span class=\"small\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/unclekam.seafood/posts/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2Funclekam.seafood%2Fposts%2F&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHb3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=6d628505\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/unclekam.seafood/posts/</a></span> 💎曹永廉💎 <span class=\"small\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/曹永廉-Raymond-Cho-337767847084014/posts/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2F%E6%9B%B9%E6%B0%B8%E5%BB%89-Raymond-Cho-337767847084014%2Fposts%2F&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHb3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=313dc888\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/曹永廉-Raymond-Cho-337767847084014/posts/</a></span></p> ============================================ <strong><span class=\"red\">被譽為品牌毒藥，曾經一連被四間廣告商割蓆嘅曹永廉</span></strong>，近排終於有人搵佢sell野喇！最近大台力推BigBigShop，強迫一眾偽人上「感謝祭」節目hard sell產品，撐警奀星亦都有份，<strong><span class=\"red\">邊間鋪頭咁好彩接受到奀星嘅死亡之吻？就係「金爺海鮮」啦</span></strong>恭喜你！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4462368/org/d156cf6427d41ae16518caa86345ced6.PNG/y9wVlEZJ8NbWswJQmBA7L4j6Ptj4OqVy5jlBZuY5QWY?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4462368%2Forg%2Fd156cf6427d41ae16518caa86345ced6.PNG%2Fy9wVlEZJ8NbWswJQmBA7L4j6Ptj4OqVy5jlBZuY5QWY%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=b7e30dbd&s={SIZE}\" /> <span class=\"small\">手拿一大本劇本的曹永廉在接受《娛樂新聞台》訪問時，即大呻：「好大嘢記呀&hellip;&hellip;嚇死呀！」之後，他又賣口乖稱：「我係介紹食嗰方面啦，我自己都好鍾意&hellip;&hellip;」</span></p> <p class=\"center\"> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cM1N2R6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcM1N2R6.png&h=5a8cce6c&s={SIZE}\" /> 【每日任務@ 25 Jul】 💎金爺海鮮速遞💎 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/unclekam.seafood/posts/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2Funclekam.seafood%2Fposts%2F&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHb3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=6d628505\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/unclekam.seafood/posts/</a></p> <p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AAJHRLA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAAJHRLA.jpg&h=3fbc295f&s={SIZE}\" /> 💎曹永廉💎 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/曹永廉-Raymond-Cho-337767847084014/posts/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2F%E6%9B%B9%E6%B0%B8%E5%BB%89-Raymond-Cho-337767847084014%2Fposts%2F&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHb3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=313dc888\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/曹永廉-Raymond-Cho-337767847084014/posts/</a></p> 講真，曹永廉你扮咩愛國啫，成日<strong><span class=\"red\">強調自己係中國人，但老婆仔女、外父外母、伯父都係加拿大籍</span></strong>，仲狡辯話係畀仔女去見識，宜家祖國發展得咁快，點解唔畀佢地把握發展機遇呀？講到尾咪又係祟洋媚外，覺得西洋空氣特別清新，你都不過係一個投機分子！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個Page上載唔到圖片，<span class=\"red\">可以copy條圖片link響留言</span> <a href=\"https://na.cx/i/AAJHRLA.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAAJHRLA.jpg&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHb3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=42420f0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/AAJHRLA.jpg</a> <em><span class=\"small\">Source: 壹周刊《曹永廉全家都係加拿大籍》 <a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_749252_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_749252_0&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHb3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=7bcf8362\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_749252_0&h=ce87f920\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_749252_0</a> 黨媒01《曹永廉推銷金爺海鮮》 <a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時娛樂/471182/tvb安排藝人臨時記劇本sell產品-曹永廉狂呻-好多嘢記呀\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%2F471182%2Ftvb%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%E8%97%9D%E4%BA%BA%E8%87%A8%E6%99%82%E8%A8%98%E5%8A%87%E6%9C%ACsell%E7%94%A2%E5%93%81-%E6%9B%B9%E6%B0%B8%E5%BB%89%E7%8B%82%E5%91%BB-%E5%A5%BD%E5%A4%9A%E5%98%A2%E8%A8%98%E5%91%80&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHb3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=ec03c2ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時娛樂/471182/tvb安排藝人臨時記劇本sell產品-曹永廉狂呻-好多嘢記呀</a></span></em> 留言template： <em><span class=\"gold\">無線新聞立場偏頗、時常斷章取義，多年來誤導不少港人，懇請 貴公司轉用其他銷售平台，例如HKTV mall，以免間接資助一間為中共維穩的電視台！而在 貴公司重新審視營銷策略前，我及我的親朋戚友將會盡量避免光顧 貴公司，敬請注意。</span></em> ============================================ 如果想準時收到TVB任務，一定要響Facebook同Telegram follow sayno4tvb團隊（我唔係佢地團隊），又或者<strong><span class=\"red\">得閒click入呢個Post（<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2059659\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2059659</a>）我會盡量每日更新</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> FB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno4tvb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno4tvb%2F&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHb3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=b60a