M1N2R6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcM1N2R6.png&h=5a8cce6c&s={SIZE}\" /> 【每日任務@ 25 Jul】 💎金爺海鮮速遞💎 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/unclekam.seafood/posts/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2Funclekam.seafood%2Fposts%2F&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHb3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=6d628505\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/unclekam.seafood/posts/</a></p> <p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AAJHRLA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAAJHRLA.jpg&h=3fbc295f&s={SIZE}\" /> 💎曹永廉💎 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/曹永廉-Raymond-Cho-337767847084014/posts/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2F%E6%9B%B9%E6%B0%B8%E5%BB%89-Raymond-Cho-337767847084014%2Fposts%2F&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHb3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=313dc888\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/曹永廉-Raymond-Cho-337767847084014/posts/</a></p> 講真，曹永廉你扮咩愛國啫，成日<strong><span class=\"red\">強調自己係中國人，但老婆仔女、外父外母、伯父都係加拿大籍</span></strong>，仲狡辯話係畀仔女去見識，宜家祖國發展得咁快，點解唔畀佢地把握發展機遇呀？講到尾咪又係祟洋媚外，覺得西洋空氣特別清新，你都不過係一個投機分子！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個Page上載唔到圖片，<span class=\"red\">可以copy條圖片link響留言</span> <a href=\"https://na.cx/i/AAJHRLA.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAAJHRLA.jpg&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHb3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=42420f0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/AAJHRLA.jpg</a> <em><span class=\"small\">Source: 壹周刊《曹永廉全家都係加拿大籍》 <a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_749252_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_749252_0&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHb3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=7bcf8362\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_749252_0&h=ce87f920\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_749252_0<